Saya akan kembali.

968
00:46:53,469 --> 00:46:55,296
<i>Betapa bodohnya kamu, Jay-jay!</i>

969
00:46:55,680 --> 00:46:57,557
<i>Bolehkah aku menamparmu sekali saja!</i>

970
00:46:58,057 --> 00:46:59,100
