984
00:47:54,155 --> 00:47:55,156
Aku akan pergi duluan, Jay.

985
00:47:57,200 --> 00:47:58,367
Berhati-hatilah saat pulang.

986
00:48:11,881 --> 00:48:12,882
Oh!

987
00:48:27,724 --> 00:48:29,057
Mengapa kamu di sini?

988
